Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.97,0:00:12.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史密斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.21,0:00:14.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目標已經確保了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.87,0:00:17.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 在明天早上…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.96,0:00:20.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您喝多了 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.64,0:00:23.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是這個房間
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:26.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.13,0:00:28.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.28,0:00:31.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡可不是你的房間哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.66,0:00:32.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.62,0:00:33.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.20,0:00:50.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳這傢伙是不是搞錯了什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.49,0:00:52.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可不是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.45,0:00:59.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你小子到底是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.31,0:01:02.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那還用說嗎 當然是正義的夥伴啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.77,0:01:05.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別耍帥了 快放我下來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.43,0:01:07.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想妳現在還是不要亂動比較好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.93,0:01:10.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.25,0:01:16.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.95,0:01:18.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.84,0:01:19.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是Meister乙HiME啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.20,0:01:23.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然是Meister乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.79,0:01:33.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.74,0:01:35.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見咯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.11,0:01:43.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.14,0:01:49.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.53,0:02:08.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉凱露
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.21,0:02:32.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在最後的總力戰中倖免於難的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.03,0:02:39.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將過去穿越星辰 改造行星的多數技術封印
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.16,0:02:44.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把世界託付于 與主人共享生命的有著超常能力的少女們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.40,0:02:50.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為秩序監視者的「乙HiME」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.75,0:02:53.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然經歷了幾度戰亂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.80,0:02:56.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,許多乙HiME與王失去了性命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.74,0:03:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 人們已將決定性的破滅留在了彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.99,0:03:15.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽 希芙璐的爸爸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.99,0:03:18.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.24,0:03:22.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在很遠的地方 有很重要的工作哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.29,0:03:25.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽不寂寞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.45,0:03:31.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽聽我說 希芙璐長大之後呢 要成為乙HiME哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.23,0:03:35.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成為乙HiME後幫助媽媽哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.10,0:03:37.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連同爸爸的份
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.25,0:03:41.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝妳 希芙璐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.89,0:03:59.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 希芙璐小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.78,0:04:03.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.44,0:04:04.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.54,0:04:06.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳醒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.91,0:04:07.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希芙璐·弗蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.28,0:04:12.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳是?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.55,0:04:20.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會 叔叔因為生病所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.72,0:04:22.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,介紹晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.63,0:04:25.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是布魯斯·瓦雷斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.10,0:04:27.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位是蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.88,0:04:30.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是蕾娜·夢宮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.86,0:04:36.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和妳的叔叔是舊識
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.29,0:04:39.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接受他的請求來接妳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.49,0:04:44.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說沒想到會演變成和誘拐犯戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.57,0:04:45.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些人到底是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.54,0:04:47.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.84,0:04:50.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很少有如此暴力的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:54.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 只要我們來了妳就沒什麼好擔心的了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.85,0:04:55.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.57,0:04:57.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是十分感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.58,0:05:00.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您救了我 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.69,0:05:03.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要謝的話謝她們就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.83,0:05:04.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.39,0:05:11.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾亞爾教團的修女·詩音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.70,0:05:15.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和她的乙HiME Meister拉凱露·真夜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.01,0:05:18.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾亞爾教團?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.59,0:05:21.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不會對有難者視而不見的團體
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.77,0:05:24.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在談了妳的事後說是會幫我們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.05,0:05:25.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.84,0:05:27.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.83,0:05:32.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們教團是絕對不會對迷途的羔羊坐視不管的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.03,0:05:36.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實是想要捐款的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.61,0:05:37.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說拉凱露!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.72,0:05:47.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真正的Meister乙HiME嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.22,0:05:49.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.19,0:05:52.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是夢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.23,0:05:56.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被真正的Meister乙HiME救了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.91,0:05:58.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.99,0:06:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好癢~~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.54,0:06:05.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天妳們就好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.14,0:06:07.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天就要離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.97,0:06:11.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是要去哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.23,0:06:13.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫特布魯姆王國
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.41,0:06:16.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳叔叔在那裡等著妳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.69,0:06:17.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔他?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.67,0:06:18.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.56,0:06:22.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔 能見到叔叔了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.40,0:06:32.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來幫忙拿行李吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.23,0:06:34.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Meister羌德拉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.18,0:06:35.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.33,0:06:40.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天真是幫大忙了 艾裡奧特
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.20,0:06:43.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到居然能在這裡見到身為五柱的妳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.29,0:06:44.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.31,0:06:48.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為追查西巴魯茲是我的工作嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.64,0:06:50.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這份謝禮下次我會好好還的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.77,0:06:52.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝禮?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.84,0:06:55.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 下次回到溫特之後再聯絡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.54,0:06:58.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼都可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.01,0:06:59.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.13,0:07:01.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要是我力所能及的事都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.26,0:07:02.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.24,0:07:03.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.07,0:07:04.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.88,0:07:06.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的真的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.92,0:07:08.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.55,0:07:12.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請等一下 艾裡奧特
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.43,0:07:14.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 我已經忍不住了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.21,0:07:16.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊 妳和畢業之前完全沒變嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.49,0:07:19.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才是妳自己說什麼都行的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.86,0:07:21.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這和那是兩回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.97,0:07:26.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我們已經半年沒見了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.68,0:07:28.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是什麼啊 我們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.68,0:07:28.42,*Note,NTP,0,0,0,,注:僕たち通常指一男一女 女生間應該是私たち
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.83,0:07:30.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 蕾娜好麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.70,0:07:35.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到有趣的東西了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.74,0:07:37.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乙HiME啊 那些傳言也是真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.25,0:07:42.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 像這麼熱情的都快成十八禁了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.58,0:07:44.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼那麼 拉凱露小姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.19,0:07:46.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳說我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.75,0:07:47.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.98,0:07:49.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳怎麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.30,0:07:51.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.83,0:07:54.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 詩音醬吃醋了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.85,0:07:56.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳…妳說什麼蠢話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.90,0:08:00.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 教團不是會鞭打同性戀嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.80,0:08:02.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請不要說的那麼直白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.35,0:08:05.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詩音醬 鞭打啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.30,0:08:07.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鞭打啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.12,0:08:09.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閉嘴!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.32,0:08:12.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在的話就快來救我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.10,0:08:16.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.40,0:08:19.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在晚飯前我會來叫妳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.36,0:08:22.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了妳自身安全 不要出房間哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.06,0:08:23.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.60,0:08:33.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.88,0:08:48.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.63,0:08:52.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.69,0:08:55.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 所以說了不能開窗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.99,0:08:57.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.98,0:08:58.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.93,0:09:00.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.82,0:09:03.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是尼娜它…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.49,0:09:07.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.68,0:09:10.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 保安會馬上幫忙抓到的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.00,0:09:14.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一點而已也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.10,0:09:19.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 妳這樣很危險的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.18,0:09:24.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希芙璐小姐 連衣裙做好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.16,0:09:28.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希芙璐小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.75,0:09:30.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 妳在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.75,0:09:31.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很危險哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.15,0:09:33.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快下來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.75,0:09:41.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.48,0:09:42.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危險!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.08,0:09:59.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尼娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.79,0:10:02.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能這樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.03,0:10:03.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.43,0:10:04.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.46,0:10:07.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了呢 希芙璐小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.32,0:10:12.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 蕾娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.43,0:10:13.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可不是對得起對不起的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.88,0:10:15.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希芙璐小姐可真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.70,0:10:26.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然幹出那麼危險的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.81,0:10:29.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是昨天被誘拐的女孩應該做的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.66,0:10:32.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜小姐請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.30,0:10:33.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 連那裡也…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.19,0:10:35.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暫停 暫停
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.95,0:10:40.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 那孩子也很高興嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.04,0:10:41.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是很好麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.15,0:10:43.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希芙璐小姐!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.47,0:10:45.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.25,0:10:50.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久沒被這麼訓斥了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.82,0:10:54.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝妳救了我 蕾娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.26,0:10:58.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然乙HiME就是厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.27,0:11:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算妳刻意隱藏也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.10,0:11:03.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為那麼厲害的事就只有乙HiME能辦到嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.17,0:11:07.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和Meister艾裡奧特和拉凱露是同級生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:10.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然主人就是布魯斯先生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.36,0:11:12.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.30,0:11:15.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒能成為乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.62,0:11:18.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.09,0:11:22.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在畢業時害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.26,0:11:23.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕是?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.84,0:11:25.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.58,0:11:29.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 蕾娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.21,0:11:32.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.48,0:11:35.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.32,0:11:42.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想成為乙HiME哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.19,0:11:45.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在面試時落榜了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.57,0:11:52.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的母親曾經反對我成為乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.20,0:11:53.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳母親?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.05,0:11:58.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希芙璐小姐 妳認為乙HiME是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.47,0:12:01.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳這麼正式地問我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.93,0:12:04.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乙HiME就是暴力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.72,0:12:06.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且是非常大的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.79,0:12:10.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在加爾德羅貝上課我很愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.02,0:12:13.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也交了很多朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.61,0:12:18.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我沒有使用那力量的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:22.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,母親她也一定是知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.72,0:12:25.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 放棄了當乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.57,0:12:27.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和母親怎樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.37,0:12:31.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有見面 因為有許多事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.59,0:12:32.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很難回去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.57,0:12:35.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.11,0:12:37.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我鬧過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.43,0:12:42.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係 因為我也聽說了希芙璐小姐的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.00,0:12:43.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.19,0:12:46.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是有了像希芙璐小姐這樣的後輩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.38,0:12:47.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乙HiME也並不壞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.61,0:12:49.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好過分
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.95,0:13:04.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史密斯大人 發現目標了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.16,0:13:24.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是麼 不會錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.20,0:13:25.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.22,0:13:28.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有數個阿斯瓦德的生化人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.14,0:13:31.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,頗有組織規模的在行動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.37,0:13:32.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.87,0:13:35.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾裡奧特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.53,0:13:40.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那個女孩落入西巴魯茲手裡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.72,0:13:41.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就殺了她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.61,0:13:44.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.84,0:13:46.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,維持現在的局面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.44,0:13:50.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我們真祖大人的乙HiME的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.56,0:13:53.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是… 在她的身邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.89,0:13:57.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己要對自己的任務抱有信心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.20,0:13:59.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀河之藍玉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.03,0:14:01.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.64,0:14:07.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.97,0:14:16.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是夏姆洛克
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.79,0:14:18.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下令C5開始
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:30.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.13,0:14:39.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我還不習慣這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.84,0:14:41.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是做夢一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.50,0:14:43.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.21,0:14:45.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼就得好好享受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.46,0:14:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請伸出手 公主
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.60,0:14:51.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.00,0:15:02.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主險些就被擊沉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.89,0:15:04.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓人一眼就看穿的孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.68,0:15:06.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不能被騙啊 希芙璐小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.44,0:15:08.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.65,0:15:10.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好慢啊 艾裡醬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.65,0:15:11.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.32,0:15:13.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 艾裡奧特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.04,0:15:14.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳的臉色不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.99,0:15:18.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼 好 去吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.87,0:15:21.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 我肚子都咕咕叫了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.42,0:15:27.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.90,0:15:39.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奴獸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.22,0:15:41.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然在這裡使用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.78,0:15:47.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希芙璐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.96,0:15:48.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.34,0:15:48.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜醬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.20,0:15:54.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位乙HiME 這裡就交給妳們了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.09,0:15:57.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託妳了 拉凱露
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.70,0:15:59.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.65,0:16:01.82,*Materialise,NTP,0,0,0,,{\4c&H272FFE&}{\3c&H7B1FDE&}Materialise!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.19,0:16:10.08,*Materialise,NTP,0,0,0,,{\4c&H272FFE&}{\3c&HB9813A&}Materialise!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.47,0:16:46.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微休息下吧 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.13,0:16:48.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種程度的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.48,0:16:50.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉凱露她們馬上就能轟走的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.89,0:16:51.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.28,0:16:54.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.00,0:16:57.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明那麼害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.40,0:16:59.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但和蕾娜在一起卻真的感覺會沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.51,0:17:01.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.03,0:17:05.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希芙璐小姐的性格太過少女向了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.65,0:17:07.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.83,0:17:10.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去和母親和好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.43,0:17:12.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個人去覺得為難的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.87,0:17:13.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我陪妳一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.34,0:17:17.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這時太放鬆了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.51,0:17:21.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜總散發著一種讓人放不下心的感覺嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.60,0:17:26.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我媽媽稍稍有些像
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.76,0:17:27.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希芙璐小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.31,0:17:33.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希芙璐小姐!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.78,0:17:38.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布魯斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.97,0:17:39.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.76,0:17:40.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.93,0:17:49.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布魯斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.15,0:17:50.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被包圍了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.46,0:17:52.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們又見面了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.16,0:17:56.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次 是將軍了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.76,0:18:04.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡的乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.20,0:18:06.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擁有赤之刃的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.61,0:18:10.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以吾之名將妳那力量解放
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.11,0:18:11.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.65,0:18:13.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.66,0:18:15.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在需要妳的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.40,0:18:17.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.40,0:18:22.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.43,0:18:36.37,*Materialise,NTP,0,0,0,,{\4c&H272FFE&}{\3c&H7667F9&}Materialise!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.98,0:18:51.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.52,0:18:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孤高的紅翡翠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.61,0:19:00.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是蕾娜·賽亞茲麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.45,0:19:03.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們在發什麼呆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.90,0:19:04.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還不快攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.19,0:19:08.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.07,0:19:10.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.17,0:19:16.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 不勝惶恐 請你們忍耐一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.46,0:19:19.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分神的話就會死哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.38,0:19:22.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.66,0:19:37.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧 愕天王
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.64,0:19:51.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老大被…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.95,0:20:00.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.95,0:20:04.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉德大人 奴獸因為害怕而不受控制了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.68,0:20:05.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.75,0:20:09.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就先饒了你們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.73,0:20:20.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希芙璐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.99,0:20:24.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們都別動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.37,0:20:27.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.14,0:20:30.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布魯斯·溫特布魯姆殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.07,0:20:33.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,約翰·史密斯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.34,0:20:35.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.63,0:20:39.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然有些倉促 不過就讓你們看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.99,0:20:41.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「編織者」的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.50,0:20:44.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.65,0:20:50.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.42,0:20:53.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.39,0:21:01.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 M-9
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.93,0:21:04.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狀態怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.78,0:21:05.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,良好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.12,0:21:07.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 有任務
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.32,0:21:11.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去排除妳面前的紅色乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.71,0:21:12.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.65,0:21:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布魯斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.79,0:21:17.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.28,0:21:42.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.52,0:21:48.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好看吧希芙璐·弗蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.72,0:21:52.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加爾德羅貝建校以來的怪物動真格是什麼樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.27,0:22:28.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.19,0:22:36.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.22,0:22:39.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Meister GEM也不行嗎 蕾娜醬
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.05,0:22:40.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
